                    "lettrine": {
                      "value": false
                    },
                    "title": {
                      "value": "First-party cookies"
                    },
                    "titleColor": {
                      "value": ""
                    },
                    "text": {
                      "value": "<p>These cookies are set by rolex.org, in order to ease your navigation and remember your settings. </p>\n<p><em>Cookie name</em> / rolex-org_lang<br />\n<em>Cookie purpose</em> / This cookie is used to determine the language used to navigate the website.<br />\n<em>Cookie expiration</em> / 1 year <br />\n<em>Storage</em> / This cookie is stored under the .rolex.org & spirit.rolex.cn domains.</p>\n<p><em>Cookie name</em> / coveo_visitorId<br />\n<em>Cookie purpose</em> / This cookie is used to identify a visitor and track their interactions on the site, to personalize search experiences and recommendations based on preferences and browsing history on that specific site.<br />\n<em>Cookie expiration</em> / 1 year <br />\n<em>Storage</em> / This cookie is stored under the.rolex.org & .rolex.cn domains.</p>"
                    },
                    "textColor": {
                      "value": ""
                    },
                    "usText": {
                      "value": ""
                    },
                    "blackText": {
                      "value": false
                    },
                    "blackBackground": {
